{"tid":1878531,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「23條來臨」趙博：國家領導人夏寶龍接任，23條蠢蠢欲動，北京對港強硬路線勢必鞏固","createTime":"2020-02-13T16:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T10:49:45.000Z","uid":13388,"like":361,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"66c0877dd475cb8e1f90fea2cf123496fc4c37ed","tid":1878531,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ogkyXAk6nUU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FogkyXAk6nUU&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=fe2bf3be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ogkyXAk6nUU</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講：<br />\n1. 夏寶龍上任，意識形態再加強，用藍絲KOL宣傳，大打文宣戰。<br />\n2. 會再推國民教育。<br />\n3. 中宣部加強，多撚左好多 西門梓敬呢D 19 藍絲KOL，意圖洗廢老腦，最近多好多人睇就咁解。<br />\n4. 為9月立法會準備，拎番過半數奶共少數派席位，更想拎三分二否決權。<br />\n5. 拎三分二否決權，從而強推 23條。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有一樣野佢地無算到，<br />\n就係武漢肺炎既影響，<br />\n自己地方都未搞好，就想搞香港<br />\n太天真了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係各位香港人要繼續留意<br />\n之前有預言6月運動個強勢會番番黎<br />\n咁都似要強推23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正評加幫手推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\